text.tspan: 4° cut line for sloping squat toilet
pattern is for 1/2 of skirt. Shift sideways, repeat it
cut solid line (top edge of skirt)
cut a strip of ~0.15- plastic, 2044 x 500
bring ends together into a loop
roll loop until it tightens around side of flap at C and stops rolling
fold loop at opposite end, then
fold it under till it stops rolling at D and meets other fold at C
cut a strip of ~0.15- plastic, 2044 x 410 (or same length as leg)
apply 25- masking tape halfway on a long edge
tape an end down the middle of a leg, long edge against underside of platform
tape top of plastic to leg, insides of front and back, and underside oftape the top to
cut solid line (top edge of skirt)
